{"tid":1103423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲你們一齊去 意大利電影節專頁 講(丁可欣)中學時期做過甚麼事","createTime":"2019-04-12T11:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T10:10:01.000Z","uid":191047,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7c728c4bedb3f469acee8207d92d5e711e09ef22","tid":1103423,"uid":191047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MR1nqc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMR1nqc0.jpg&h=bead76a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">識英文嘅各位<br />\n呼籲你們一齊去<br />\n意大利電影節專頁<br />\n講丁可欣中學時期做過甚麼事<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">呢到打咗一篇<br />\n大家隨便copy</span></span><br />\n<br />\nI would like to inform you something regarding to Actress Yanki Ting.<br />\n<br />\nYears ago, she stole her schoolmates&rsquo; mobile phone, she also bullied and hurt her schoolmates and that affected her schoolmates&rsquo; mental health. <br />\n<br />\nShe only apologised when she got exposed. We do not think her apology is sincere and an apology video is not enough. <br />\n<br />\nWe do not tolerate this kind of disgsuting, inhumane behaviour. It&rsquo;s been months but until now, the authorities haven&rsquo;t take any actions yet. <br />\n<br />\nAs a concerned citizen, we would like for you to think twice about inviting her to the Italy film event. <br />\n<br />\nThousands and millions of people are suffering depression and anxiety because of bullying. If you&rsquo;re still considering inviting her to the event after reading this, that means you guys support bullying and that means you are a part of the problem.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">(意大利電影節個Facebook )</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/64396356785/posts/10155959642056786\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F64396356785%2Fposts%2F10155959642056786&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8DKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=5a08594f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/64396356785/posts/10155959642056786</a>"},{"pid":"6006178f88a10f167366a18f08a8c785fda2c717","tid":1103423,"uid":191047,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQy1FRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQy1FRE.jpg&h=5d53d762&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb5024b1ae9b99f0b4580ecc30ec2ea94ff1991b","tid":1103423,"uid":191047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979be78a846062c28a9d9cec5cc40d4c5700bdb8","tid":1103423,"uid":191047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">洗底欣開始做嘢啦</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KH2azcY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKH2azcY.jpg&h=1b159bbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"773af9cc30b2671f8ec2dd81a1ca2589a7309b7d","tid":1103423,"uid":41524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:54:31.000Z","msg":"學人講道德!?笑到我仆街"},{"pid":"b4317996520e53660d2075b210f011169ffd76a6","tid":1103423,"uid":191047,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T12:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9iJQzik.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9iJQzik.jpg&h=26161cac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"p